{"title":"Save $80 on the Apple Watch Series 6 in stunning (Product) RED","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/342727/save-80-on-the-apple-watch-series-6-in-stunning-product-red.html","date":1617813053000,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<html><body><div id=\"link_wrapped_content\">\n<section class=\"wp-block-bigbite-multi-title\"><div class=\"container\"></div></section><p>With warmer weather approaching, we&rsquo;re all starting to think about getting back in shape. And there&rsquo;s no better companion than the Apple Watch Series 6. And today we&rsquo;ve got a great deal on it. <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/New-Apple-Watch-GPS-40mm-Aluminum/dp/B08J5RBMRN?th=1&amp;#038;tag=macworld05-20?tag=macworld05-20\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.amazon.com/New-Apple-Watch-GPS-40mm-Aluminum/dp/B08J5RBMRN?th=1&amp;tag=macworld05-20\" rel=\"nofollow\">Amazon is selling the 40mm Apple Watch Series 6 in gorgeous (Product) RED for $320</a>, good for $80 off the MSRP and the lowest price we&rsquo;ve ever seen.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Apple Watch Series 6 is the Cadillac of smartwatches, with an array of features and sensors you won&rsquo;t find anywhere else. In our <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/234682/apple-watch-series-6-review.html\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/234682/apple-watch-series-6-review.html\">4.5-star review,</a> we called the Apple Watch Series 6 &ldquo;simply stellar,&rdquo; and concluded that the extra expense over the SE or the Series 3 is definitely worth it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The premium price doesn&rsquo;t just get you a cool color. The Series 6 has an ECG, blood-oxygen sensor, fall detection, sleep tracking, always-on display, sleep tracking, and a second-gen heart-rate sensor. It&rsquo;s also compatible with every previous band, so you&rsquo;ll have no shortage of fashionable options. And as an extra bonus, you get three months of Apple Fitness+ for free.</p>\n\n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-product-widget-block product-widget\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__block-title-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"product-widget__block-title\" id=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h4>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__title-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"product-widget__title\" id=\"apple-watch-series-6\">Apple Watch Series 6</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__image-outer-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__image-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"product-widget__image\" src=\"https://images.idgesg.net/images/article/2020/09/apple-watch-series-6-press-100858143-orig.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Apple Watch Series 6\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"review product-widget__review-details\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__rating-and-review-link\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__review-details--rating\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"starRating\" style=\"--rating: 4.5;\" aria-label=\"Rating of this product is 4.5 out of 5\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><a class=\"product-widget__review-link\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/234682/apple-watch-series-6-review.html\" target=\"_blank\">Read our review</a>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div classname=\"product-widget__information\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div classname=\"product-widget__information--rrp-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span classname=\"product-widget__information--rrp-label\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMSRP:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span classname=\"product-widget__information--rrp-value\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFrom $399\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"product-widget__prici